data.description: Time to own your home in the desirable Morgan's Point Resort! Depending on your offer, seller will provide up to $5,000 concessions which can be used to help buy down interest rate!  Just minutes from the water on Belton lake and Morgan's Point Resort Marina.  Inside has a large living room with stone flooring and a natural gas fireplace.  Bedrooms are all laminate flooring.  Kitchen has granite countertops, center island, white cabinets, and stainless steel appliances.  Back patio is enclosed and provided with central heat/AC and will include gas stand alone fireplace.  Out back you will find and extended wood deck and 2 storage sheds that are hooked up to electricity.  There is also a side entry in the fence to the backyard that will allow you to store a boat or RV with a 30 amp plug to plug in if needed.  Schedule a showing today before this one is gone.
